# Render Environment Variables Templates

## Backend Web Service Environment Variables
```
NODE_ENV=production
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://hp6173585:harsh123@cluster0.jlvsoq2.mongodb.net/trackmint?retryWrites=true&w=majority
JWT_SECRET=change-this-to-a-super-secure-production-secret-key
JWT_EXPIRE=7d
CORS_ORIGIN=https://your-frontend-site-name.onrender.com
```

## Frontend Static Site Environment Variables
```
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-service-name.onrender.com/api
VITE_FINNHUB_API_KEY=d2nar4pr01qn3vmk8j90d2nar4pr01qn3vmk8j9g
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyDzAfYtlht_MpW1JMQhq0kSEtFU6Fm7Uvs
```

## Deployment Order
1. Deploy Backend first → Get backend URL
2. Deploy Frontend with backend URL → Get frontend URL  
3. Update Backend CORS_ORIGIN with frontend URL
4. Redeploy Backend

## Quick Deploy Commands (for reference)
```bash
# Backend (handled by Render)
npm install
npm start

# Frontend (handled by Render)
cd frontend
npm install
npm run build
```